'''''Challenge'' 56''' was a roleplaying magazine from January of [[1992]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including a rules supplement for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Power Suits! New Skills and Combat Rules]]" and was written by [[Paul Sudlow]].

